folder: Pelham Parkway North & Lodovick Avenue, Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: Pelham Parkway North - Lodovick Avenue
text:
Pelham Parkway North (running directly in front of the white house), at the N.E. corner of Lodovick Ave., showing the William T. Burke real
estate office.
August 3, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
